Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是在和谁战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙  难道比藤堂还要...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德
